Class HubValidateListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.hub.HubListenerAdapter
      • com.viaoa.hub.HubValidateListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HubListener, EventListener

    public class HubValidateListener
extends HubListenerAdapter
    Validation listener that can be used for beforeXxx events. Throw an exception to have the hub not perform the operation.

    vvia

        public void beforePropertyChange(HubEvent e)
        Description copied from interface: HubListener
        Event sent whenever a property is changed. This includes OAObject or Hub properties.
        OAObject: any object property, changed, editable, new
        Hub: allowDelete, allowNew, allowEdit, eof, bof
